                            <rubric>Knytlinga Saga <lb/> ſeu <lb/> Rerum Danicarum Historia ab anno
                                Christi <lb/> 1043 ad annum 1187</rubric>
                            <incipit>Sveirn Son Ulfs Jarls tök Jarldöm af Magnue <lb/> konge
                                Olafſsyne</incipit>
                            <filiation>On the title page <name type="person" key="ArnMag001">Árni
                                    Magnússon</name> informs that this volume is a transcript of
                                manuscript belonging to <name type="person" key="WilWor001">Willum
                                    Worm</name>. A note on the flyleaf, possibly in <name type="person" key="BirTho001">Birger Thorlacius</name>’ hand,
                                states that the text of AM 20 h fol is identical with the text of
                                latter manuscript.</filiation>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
